Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.55,0:00:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.94,0:00:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.65,0:00:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.05,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.35,0:00:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.31,0:00:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.96,0:02:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.10,0:02:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一個通過與同契者同契成為強大力量的種族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.40,0:02:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其中被稱為最強種族的七煌寶樹之一 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.15,0:02:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及和她締結契約的人類少年 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.56,0:02:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩個人朝著傳說之地煌珠樂園踏上了旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.71,0:03:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早飯做好了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.68,0:03:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.21,0:03:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該先說早上好吧 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.17,0:03:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第六唱 凝視同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,311
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.12,0:03:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,311
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.98,0:03:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,312
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,312
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.68,0:03:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,313
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,313
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.80,0:03:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,340
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,340
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.87,0:03:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼313了之後就是340了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.46,0:03:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 剛才到多少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受夠了 不做了 不做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種特訓根本一點意義都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.86,0:03:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算對酷沒意義對蕾還是有意義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.28,0:03:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.82,0:04:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為酷而讓蕾陷入險境也不要緊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了就繼續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.23,0:04:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從157開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,150...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼變一半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才停了所以減少一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不快點開始的話再少一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.01,0:04:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,150...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.88,0:04:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 一點也不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.86,0:04:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看 看 這樣都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.32,0:04:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,158 159 160 161
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.31,0:04:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論做多少都是小菜一碟 沒事沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.67,0:04:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我吃好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.24,0:04:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為肚子餓了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.46,0:04:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍 烹飪技術又提高了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.84,0:04:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷不吃沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.92,0:05:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事 待會兒再吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.09,0:05:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼點特訓就累趴下了看來還差得遠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.93,0:05:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下來我還要出去洗碗筷就交給大家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.49,0:05:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天打工很急嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.30,0:05:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老闆說給我加工資了叫我能不能早點去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是我的後輩 龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.91,0:05:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,短短一星期就賺了這麼多還加工資了 了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.60,0:05:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加油盡量地多賺點旅費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的零食費也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.12,0:05:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說起來 龍在打什麼工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總是在晚上出門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.05,0:05:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼說來到底是什麼零工呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.31,0:05:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然讓他去了計時工資最豐厚的地方面試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.98,0:05:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望不要是什麼不正當的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有誰還要下注嗎 下注了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.92,0:05:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍威的話無論什麼都會想出辦法搞定的 不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.35,0:06:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.54,0:06:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,油燜海蟄頭 是我愛吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.47,0:06:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.95,0:06:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,醒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.68,0:06:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.90,0:06:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在就去熱熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.53,0:06:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了 這樣就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.82,0:06:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是因為 那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.76,0:06:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我吃好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.85,0:07:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.04,0:07:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.02,0:07:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,漂亮的核石啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我能坐這兒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.78,0:07:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,累死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.59,0:08:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下來 早飯的菜單...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得想好了再睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.73,0:08:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是好睏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一邊睡一邊想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 就這麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做什麼好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.14,0:08:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 再也 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,動不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.94,0:08:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毅力不夠 毅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.92,0:08:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話以後碰到強大的對手是贏不了的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對手是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.61,0:08:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.28,0:08:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事 就這點程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.99,0:08:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下來 具備了基本\N體力之後就開始正式的格鬥訓練吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩位 請同契吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.16,0:09:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.76,0:09:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是赤手空拳的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我能做那麼卑鄙的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.29,0:09:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷這種程度的對手赤手空拳就能應付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.89,0:09:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.96,0:09:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我這是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.28,0:09:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想把我殺了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.03,0:09:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是說了不要緊的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比我想的要強啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣下去很快就能大見長進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.16,0:09:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.30,0:09:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比我想的還要掌握不好分寸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,慘了 希絲卡 這該怎麼辦 能修好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.91,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這下有的忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想把我切成三片嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以說了很難控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還真能挺到現在沒被敵人打敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.12,0:10:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.97,0:10:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾長時間的睏倦不僅僅是因為封印的後遺癥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.54,0:10:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你無謂地使她消耗體力是罪魁禍首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.19,0:10:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那是在同等地增加她的負擔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.15,0:10:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.34,0:10:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 今晚是什錦魚雜煮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.36,0:10:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.77,0:10:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也沒吃就睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.77,0:11:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.45,0:11:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那個 這個真好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.31,0:11:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.66,0:11:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定會變得能保護你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.41,0:11:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,變得能戰鬥 能保護好蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.22,0:11:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.94,0:11:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是因為...還用說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.42,0:11:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾是女孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我作為男人一定要保護你的 再說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.81,0:11:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再說 老大們也吩咐過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.37,0:11:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.36,0:11:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,磨磨蹭蹭地在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.82,0:11:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,違抗的話再追加100個俯臥撐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夢...夢話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.84,0:11:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很開心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.19,0:11:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發生什麼了 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那樣的 龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.81,0:12:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 對了 我有一個請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.10,0:12:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請求？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.06,0:12:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以啊 說來聽聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.74,0:12:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,屋子裏一個人都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.79,0:12:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到時間了酷也沒出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.81,0:12:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這應該認為是討厭特訓而溜了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.58,0:12:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肯定是因為這段時間沒實戰所以放鬆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.01,0:12:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種情況到底還是需要有強大的對手出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.80,0:12:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同契者之間的戰鬥還是得問同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.44,0:12:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對煌珠來說也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.16,0:12:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,疼 疼 疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.93,0:13:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.24,0:13:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個頭箍在酷想要\N使出過多的力量時就會刺激你的痛覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,疼的不止是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.24,0:13:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.63,0:13:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.41,0:13:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍威 不能改改嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只讓我一個人痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.16,0:13:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.60,0:13:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.22,0:13:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干的話立即現金支付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.33,0:13:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過得在得手之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.35,0:13:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,意下如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.54,0:13:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瞧你 握得太緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天就先到此為止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.47,0:13:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒累趴下之前收手也是進步的秘訣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這兒睡的話會感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾 我會更加努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光努力是不夠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.70,0:14:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼時候坐那兒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.81,0:14:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人生之路也是很漫長的 慢慢來也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.98,0:14:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有好好想著蕾嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.49,0:14:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.99,0:14:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒看到 我什麼都沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.65,0:14:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在問蕾所想的事你有沒有好好去理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.05,0:14:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.41,0:14:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和煌珠同契 是有點像談戀愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.47,0:14:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,談戀愛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.56,0:14:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,單方面一相情願就只是單戀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.54,0:15:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得好好體會對方的情感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.03,0:15:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別焦躁 好好努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.19,0:15:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是關鍵時刻別猶豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是大姐我的建議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.94,0:15:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇雅和龍威是戀人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.71,0:15:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.92,0:15:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.35,0:15:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍完全不是我喜歡的類型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那為什麼和龍威締結契約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.29,0:15:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為他絕對不是我會喜歡上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.91,0:15:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.26,0:15:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要有決心的 喜歡人什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷還不需要懂這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.97,0:15:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 還不需要懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.94,0:16:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然敢逃我制定的特訓 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.99,0:16:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 偶爾也是要休息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天的事就不跟你計較
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.36,0:16:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 不像希絲卡的作風啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.29,0:16:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,平時的話嘰嘰咕咕地教訓個不停聽得耳朵都起繭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.81,0:16:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.01,0:16:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒 什麼都沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.13,0:16:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 看到龍留的小紙條了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.94,0:16:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天也要早點去打工 大家隨便吃點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.09,0:16:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肚子早就餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,馬上吃晚飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.73,0:16:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天會是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.63,0:16:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這些是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.62,0:16:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於強大的對手出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.65,0:17:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣稍微有點危機感的話肯定又會認真地進行特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.93,0:17:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又可說是實戰演習 簡直一舉兩得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.38,0:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.64,0:17:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.35,0:17:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好勒 上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.30,0:17:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.28,0:17:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了 還戴著頭箍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個鑰匙在龍那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣可就使不出全力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對於地痞來說身手還挺不錯的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣 做得太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再動手的話就不付報酬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.76,0:17:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.78,0:17:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡 居然追到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.60,0:17:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,擬煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.52,0:18:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡 他們也同契了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.31,0:18:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.26,0:18:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下 我來做你的對手 一對一的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.64,0:18:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我都說了一對一了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.99,0:18:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.05,0:18:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想起來燉的那鍋裏忘記放生奶油了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.31,0:18:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就因為這個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷 頭箍的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.88,0:18:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.96,0:18:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.08,0:18:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾 你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.18,0:18:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.72,0:18:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得幫幫酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇雅 同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.48,0:19:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.94,0:19:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,頭箍沒反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.86,0:19:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經不用替那兩個人擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.13,0:19:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.86,0:19:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好體會對方的情感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.32,0:19:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾 助我一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.25,0:19:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和我一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,潛藏於暗夜之中{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.08,0:19:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所侍奉之青龍{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.11,0:19:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心之澄境蘊風雲{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.13,0:19:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,漩風飛速聚集{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.02,0:19:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黎明前之朦月{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,汝與我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.46,0:19:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心意互通{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這頌詞是新的招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.29,0:19:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 挺厲害的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.26,0:19:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南風之弦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.91,0:19:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,厲害 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.22,0:19:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.64,0:20:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼短的特訓時間就讓酷使出這麼大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.79,0:20:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.36,0:20:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 那位大姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.99,0:20:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要恫嚇哪個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.09,0:20:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弄壞了屋子被趕了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.45,0:20:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好不容易龍威賺來的錢也作為修理屋子之用全沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒辦法的事 前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.54,0:20:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一邊旅行一邊再找工作好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.79,0:20:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無聊的把戲再莫名其妙地搞出來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.43,0:20:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要怪也得怪酷沒來特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.91,0:20:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.81,0:20:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找個能避雨的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.78,0:20:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.42,0:20:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在雨中淋淋不是什麼壞事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.51,0:22:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隱藏在溫和儒雅的微笑背後的思緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.98,0:22:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無法越過隔閡的苦惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.39,0:22:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下回 並唱頌之決意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.50,0:23:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第七唱 並唱頌之決意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.39,0:23:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少年和少女有了些改變

